":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0d2e849160cc65993248d1e06924ef84aaf5db1","tid":1818973,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:08:16.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=7d69a859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"8a95a8cc79761188827eddbd3576b01e41ad3823","tid":1818973,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1e8bff985afaee3609ec9be913821ed7a5d2da3","tid":1818973,"uid":232583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f02c3c55227a01b4de351ada1f3b6fd498e1a0ff","tid":1818973,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:34:55.000Z","msg":"睇醫生診斷必須<br />\n定期做啲psychotherapies 唔好去去吓唔去<br />\n做運動 set目標跑吓步<br />\n同身邊朋友傾吓<br />\n盡量早啲休息早啲起身 食早餐開始新一日<br />\n嚴重就要堅持食藥一段日子"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:41:20.000Z","msg":"係咩要去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T09:50:09.000Z","msg":"睇醫生先判斷到你係咪真係情緒病架嘛<br />\n或者揾坊間嘅輔導員/社工 傾下 <br />\n有需要會建議你睇醫生"}]}